    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>The code below should work.</p>\n\n<pre><code>public class B implements A {\n    @Override\n    public void foo() {\n        System.out.println(\"B.foo\");\n    }\n\n    void aFoo() {\n        A.super.foo();\n    }\n\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        B b = new B();\n        b.foo();\n        b.aFoo();\n    }\n}\n\ninterface A {\n    default void foo() {\n        System.out.println(\"A.foo\");\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Output:</p>\n\n<pre><code>B.foo\nA.foo\n</code></pre>\n"
